  "html": "<h1>Applies to</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>PCI DSS Requirement 5.1.1</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <h1>What to Check For</h1>\r\n  <p>All installed anti-virus programs should detect, remove, and protect against all known types of malware.</p>\r\n  <h1>How to Check</h1>\r\n  <p>Refer to the vendor's web site, documentation&amp;nbsp;or tech support to verify that your anti-virus can detect, remove, and protect against viruses, trojans, worms, spyware, adware, and rootkits.</p>\r\n  <h1>How to Fix</h1>\r\n  <p>If your anti-virus does not adequately handle all known types of malware threats, install and configure an anti-virus that does. In some cases, updating the anti-virus to the latest version may be sufficient.</p>\r\n  <h1>Related Items</h1>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <a href=\"/article/6a12327a-3bc3-4acc-af65-9145046280b9\">Deploy an Anti-Virus</a>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>"
